Class MediaMaker

  • java.lang.Object
    • MediaMaker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<MediaMaker>

    public class MediaMaker
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<MediaMaker>
    This class will instantiate MediaMaker objects which contain information about a specific person such as their name, which number of that name they are, their acting credentials (if any), their directing credentials (if any), and their producing credentials (if any)
